column1: 65,"prefix dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> select distinct ?title, ?pict, ?label, ?abstract where {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andronikos_II_Palaiologos> dbpo:title ?title ; foaf:depiction ?pict ; rdfs:label ?label ; dbpo:abstract ?abstract FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = ""en"" )}"
